UID:1a026205-0a8a-4761-bd43-e8856f7bf201@1a02.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<p></p><p><b>Every Wednesday</b> from <b>7pm until midnight</b> the diversity Bar takes place in our diversity Café!</p><p>It is open every Wednesday to all youth and young adults under 27\, whether lesbian\, gay\, bisexual\, trans*\, inter*\, non-binary\, aro/ace or straight!</p><p><b>Bring all your friends!</b></p><p>Meet like-minded young LGBTIAQ* youth under 27 at the diversity Bar with a comfortable atmosphere\, delicious drinks\, and good vibes\, and enjoy a queer evening at affordable youth prices.</p><p>As usual\, you can get soft drinks from €1.70 and alcoholic drinks from €2.30.</p><h4>Contact us!</h4><p>If you&#x27\;d like to contact our diversity Bar team directly\, if you&#x27\;re interested in occasionally working at the diversity Bar and mixing drinks\, helping to shape the diversity Bar\, and becoming part of the diversity Bar team\, then get in touch with us <a href="https://diversity-muenchen.de/en/diversity-cafe/contact-diversity-bar/"><b>using the contact form</b></a> or just talk to us during opening hours! More information about the diversity Bar is available <a id="7" linktype="page">here</a>.</p><p><b>We are very much looking forward to hearing from you and – hopefully soon – welcoming you as part of our team.</b></p>\n\n(Error: The event had no end date)
DURATION:PT2H57M
LOCATION:diversity Café\, Blumenstraße 29\, 80331\, München
DTSTART:20250806T170000Z
SUMMARY:diversity Bar
UID:70d76b2f-e31d-4bdf-97e3-06d6d8f2878a@70d7.org
END:VEVENT
