UID:9efe4767-f00c-4f87-8c28-6b7ee9e7d6c1@9efe.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<p>  </p><p>Our relaxed café afternoon for everyone up to 27 years old. You can meet your friends in a quiet atmosphere or get to know other LGBTIAQ* youth in the afternoon or over the weekend.</p><p>Our diverse team hosts our youth café and treats you to all kinds of cold and hot drinks as well as hearty and sweet food at our usual low prices.</p><p><b>Our diversity Café opens regularly:</b></p><ul><li>every Tuesday from 4 pm. to 8      pm.</li><li>every Thursday from 4 pm to 8      pm and</li><li>every Sunday from 3 pm to 7 pm</li></ul><p>You can also find up-to-date information on social media (e.g. in the event of short-term closures).</p><p><b>Contact us!</b></p><p>If you’d like to get in touch with our diversity Café directly – for example\, if you’d like to volunteer or organise a small event with us at the diversity Café (such as a reading\, concert or poetry slam) – then contact us <b>using the contact form</b> or talk to us at during opening hours.</p><p><b>We are happy about active support and show you as a beginner everything in a relaxed way.</b></p>
DTEND:20250812T180000Z
LOCATION:diversity Café\, Blumenstraße 29\, 80331\, München
DTSTART:20250812T140000Z
SUMMARY:diversity Café
